snippet.title: Sticky Business: Plan With Me DLC - Official Announcement Trailer | Wholesome Snack 2023
snippet.description: Watch the latest trailer for Sticky Business to see what to expect with the upcoming Plan With Me DLC, which brings more stories, goodies, stickers, and more tied to an office theme to the small business simulation game. Sticky Business' Plan With Me DLC will be available on PC on December 18, 2023.
